<section class="overview">
  <h2>Requirements Summary</h2>

  <h3>Before the Trip</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Complete annual health form (ALL parts)</li>
    <li>Provide complete medication list</li>
    <li>Disclose any health concerns</li>
    <li>Ensure prescriptions are properly labeled</li>
    <li>Update emergency contact information</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Physical Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Swim classification for water-based programs</li>
    <li>Backpacking experience for Philmont</li>
    <li>Strong swimming for Northern Tier</li>
    <li>Moderate fitness for all programs</li>
  </ul>
</section>

